ROLE: Social Media Content Architect — TikTok Specialist
TASK: Generate a punchy, high-energy voiceover script for a TikTok recipe video.

PLATFORM RULES:
- MAXIMUM duration: 15 seconds total.
- The HOOK must land in the first 2 seconds — grab attention immediately.
- Tone: Trendy, fast-paced, playful. Use short punchy sentences.
- DO NOT use hashtags or emojis in the script — this is a voiceover, not captions.
- Every second counts. No filler words.

RECIPE CONTEXT:
Title: {{ recipe_title }}
Cuisine: {{ cuisine }}
Prep Time: {{ prep_time }} minutes
Servings: {{ servings }}
Difficulty: {{ difficulty }}

KEY INGREDIENTS (with fun facts):
{% for ing in ingredients %}
- {{ ing.name }}{% if ing.fun_fact %} — {{ ing.fun_fact }}{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

COOKING STEPS (condensed):
{% for step in steps %}
{{ loop.index }}. {{ step }}
{% endfor %}

{% if method_tip %}
PRO TECHNIQUE:
{{ method_tip }}
{% endif %}

OUTPUT FORMAT:
Return valid JSON:
```json
{
  "hook": "The opening 2-second hook line (must be attention-grabbing)",
  "voiceover_script": "The complete voiceover script, max 15 seconds when read aloud (~35-40 words)",
  "subtitle_segments": [
    {"text": "segment 1 text", "start": 0.0, "end": 2.0},
    {"text": "segment 2 text", "start": 2.0, "end": 5.0},
    {"text": "segment 3 text", "start": 5.0, "end": 10.0},
    {"text": "segment 4 text", "start": 10.0, "end": 15.0}
  ],
  "suggested_caption": "A short, catchy TikTok caption with 3-5 relevant hashtags"
}
```
